〈'''另一个人'''〉<ref>{{cite AV media |title=老菸槍雙人組 The Chainsmokers / 另一個人 Somebody (HD中字MV) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xKYxdtLeWuw |language=zh |deadurl=no |date=2018-05-03 |accessdate=2021-01-20 |publisher=台灣索尼音樂 Sony Music Taiwan YouTube 頻道 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210120100803/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xKYxdtLeWuw |archivedate=2021-01-20 }}</ref>（{{lang-en|"Somebody"}}）是美国[[唱片骑师|DJ]][[烟鬼组合|烟鬼组合]]主唱，[[R&B|R&B]]组合{{tsl|en|THEY.}}成员德鲁·洛夫伴唱的单曲。歌曲由安德鲁·塔格特、德鲁·洛夫及{{tsl|en|Emily Warren|埃米莉·沃伦}}填词作曲，烟鬼组合负责制作，并于2018年4月20日通过{{tsl|en|Disruptor Records|破坏者唱片}}和[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]发行。〈另一个人〉是烟鬼组合第二部[[录音室专辑|录音室专辑]]《[[厌世男孩_(专辑)|厌世男孩]]》中的第四首单曲。

==发行==
2018年4月18日，烟鬼组合曝光了单曲作品并公布了发行日期<ref>{{cite news|last=Meadow|first=Matthew|title=The Chainsmokers Announce New Music This Friday… And It Has A Featured Vocalist!|url=https://www.youredm.com/2018/04/18/the-chainsmokers-announce-new-music-this-friday-and-it-has-a-featured-vocalist/|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=Your EDM|date=2018-04-18|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111234/https://www.youredm.com/2018/04/18/the-chainsmokers-announce-new-music-this-friday-and-it-has-a-featured-vocalist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。〈另一个人〉是一首结合了[[流行_(音乐类型)|流行]]、[[当代节奏布鲁斯|R&B]]和[[电子舞曲|EDM]]元素的热带音乐<ref>{{cite news|last=McNeilage|first=Ross|title=New Music Round-Up: Ariana Grande, Liam Payne, Anne-Marie|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/liam-payne/news/new-music-roundup-ariana-grande-liam-payne-annemarie|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=MTV News|date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111243/http://www.mtv.co.uk/liam-payne/news/new-music-roundup-ariana-grande-liam-payne-annemarie|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Sweeney|first=Farrell|title=The Chainsmokers impress on new track 'Somebody'|url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/04/chainsmokers-impress-new-track-somebody/|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=Dancing Astronaut|date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111329/https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/04/chainsmokers-impress-new-track-somebody/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Ghanem|first=Louis|title=The Chainsmokers- Somebody (ft. Drew Love)|url=https://www.edmtunes.com/2018/04/the-chainsmokers-somebody-ft-drew-love/|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=EDMTunes|date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111311/https://www.edmtunes.com/2018/04/the-chainsmokers-somebody-ft-drew-love/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲伴着“哀伤的音调和大气的合成器声”，并由“重低音[[Drop|Drop]]”组成<ref name="Idolator">{{cite news|last=Nied|first=Mike|title=The Chainsmokers Unite With Drew Love On New Single "Somebody"|url=https://www.idolator.com/7678529/chainsmokers-drew-love-somebody|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=Idolator|date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111311/https://www.idolator.com/7678529/chainsmokers-drew-love-somebody|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[公告牌|公告牌]]》的凯特·贝因（Kat Bein）称歌曲为“充满了R&B音调的慢工之作，闪动的特点让人想起烟鬼组合早期的作品”<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=The Chainsmokers & Drew Love From THEY. Teamed Up For 'Somebody'|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8347159/the-chainsmokers-somebody-drew-love-they|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=Billboard|date=2018-04-18|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111238/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8347159/the-chainsmokers-somebody-drew-love-they|dead-url=no}}</ref>。词曲方面，这首歌“讲述了当周围的人都专注于用物质包围自己时，保持真实自我的艰难和重要性”<ref name="CelebMix">{{cite news|last=Rees|first=Katrina|title=The Chainsmokers release new track 'Somebody' with Drew Love|url=https://celebmix.com/the-chainsmokers-somebody-drew-love/|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=CelebMix|date=2018-04-21|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111238/https://celebmix.com/the-chainsmokers-somebody-drew-love/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==评价==
{{tsl|en|Idolator (website)|Idolator}}网站的迈克·尼德（Mike Nied）认为〈另一个人〉是“二人在2018年最强势的作品，也是他们迄今为止最内敛的制作之一”。他称这首歌与二人此前的作品相比更加内敛，他写道：“（塔格特的）声音轻松地衬托出了伴唱歌手”<ref name="Idolator"/>。HotNewHipHop的尚蒂伊·波斯特（Chantilly Post）认为这首歌“展现了（烟鬼组合）制作平静、内敛曲调的天赋”<ref>{{cite news|last=Post|first=Chantilly|title=The Chainsmokers Grab Drew Love On "Somebody"|url=https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/the-chainsmokers-grab-drew-love-on-somebody-new-song.1978266.html|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=HotNewHipHop|date=2018-04-21|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119111252/https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/the-chainsmokers-grab-drew-love-on-somebody-new-song.1978266.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==音乐视频==
〈另一个人〉的[[音乐视频|音乐视频]]由吉姆·巴特（Jim Batt）和{{tsl|en|Kim Boekbinder|金·伯克宾德}}执导，并配有{{tsl|en|Molly Crabapple|莫莉·克拉巴普}}的延时水彩画。烟鬼组合在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上称视频“讲述了一个关于诱惑的故事，我们都在用自己的方式处理诱惑，但它往往会使我们感到费解。”<ref name="CelebMix"/>

